      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Unreferenced|date=March 2010}}
A '''computer expo''' is a [[trade fair]] or exposition for computers and electronics. Expos usually include company or organization booths where products and technologies are demonstrated; talks and lectures; and general mixing of people with common interests.

*[[CeBIT]]
*[[COMDEX]]
*[[Computex Taipei]]
*[[Computer World Expo]]
*[[GITEX]]
*[[HostingCon]]
*[[Interop]]
*[[LinuxTag]]
*[[Macworld Conference &amp; Expo]]
*[http://www.theswcc.org Southwest Computer Conference &amp; Expo]
*[[SMAU]]
*[[Unified Communications Expo]]
*[[SIMO]]
[[Category:Computer conferences|*]]

